could be right for you.

48:19.689 --> 48:21.232
Yeah, how'd you do?

48:21.316 --> 48:23.943
Perfect score.
Twenty out of 20.

48:24.027 --> 48:25.862
"Have holidays or gatherings

48:25.945 --> 48:28.740
ever been spoiled
by a loved one's drinking?"

48:28.823 --> 48:30.158
Yeah.

48:30.241 --> 48:31.826
"Have you ever called
the police

48:31.910 --> 48:33.411
for fear of abuse?"

48:33.494 --> 48:35.788
The best ones
are at the bottom.

48:35.872 --> 48:38.958
"Do you feel more alive
in the midst of a crisis?"

48:39.042 --> 48:40.376
Mm-hmm.

48:40.460 --> 48:42.045
"Are you uneasy when your life

48:42.128 --> 48:44.505
is going smoothly?"
Mm-hmm.

48:44.589 --> 48:46.132
And my personal favorite:

48:46.215 --> 48:47.842
"Do you care for others easily,

48:47.926 --> 48:50.428
but find it difficult
to care for yourself?"

48:52.889 --> 48:56.225
You might need to start going
to two groups a day now.

48:56.309 --> 48:58.895
Yeah.
It's fucked up.

49:00.813 --> 49:03.524
I was doing so well
for a while.

49:05.234 --> 49:07.487
I really thought
I had a chance.

49:09.322 --> 49:11.074
You do have a chance.

49:15.912 --> 49:18.456
I don't know
if I believe that anymore.

49:22.210 --> 49:24.212
I don't know what happened.

49:24.754 --> 49:27.465
It just all fell apart so fast.

49:34.931 --> 49:37.350
I don't really know
what I'm supposed to do now.

49:39.352 --> 49:41.646
Only thing you can do.

49:43.189 --> 49:44.941
You get back up.

49:46.150 --> 49:48.236
You start over.

49:50.029 --> 49:51.072
It's that easy, huh?

49:51.155 --> 49:54.534
No, it's fucking hard,

49:54.617 --> 49:56.119
but you're strong.

49:58.413 --> 50:00.039
Are you sure?

50:01.833 --> 50:03.459
Yeah.

50:04.419 --> 50:05.795
I'm sure.

50:16.806 --> 50:18.307
All right.
Shit.

50:18.391 --> 50:20.601
I gotta go work.

50:20.685 --> 50:22.353
Yeah, you got a new job?

50:22.437 --> 50:23.980
Yeah.

50:24.063 --> 50:25.815
Nights at the Valero.

50:25.898 --> 50:28.276
Ho, ho!
Starting from the top, huh?

50:28.818 --> 50:30.987
Hey, um,
did you ever find Liam today?

50:31.070 --> 50:32.739
No, but Debbie was here

50:32.822 --> 50:34.699
most of the day.
She might have.

50:34.782 --> 50:35.908
All right.

50:37.160 --> 50:39.746
<i>♪♪ Don't mean
I'm gonna let go ♪♪</i>

50:39.829 --> 50:42.665
<i>♪♪ Not gonna lay down
die here ♪♪</i>

50:42.749 --> 50:44.751
<i>♪♪ There's blood
still running ♪♪</i>

50:52.216 --> 50:53.718
One
of your sisters again?

50:53.801 --> 50:55.970
Nope.
Brother.

50:59.348 --> 51:01.976
- Is that Chris Rock?
- No.

51:02.060 --> 51:04.395
Look, that lady's about
to shoot that dude in the head.

51:04.479 --> 51:06.898
I'm going up now, Todd.
You boys don't forget

51:06.981 --> 51:08.775
to brush your teeth
and say your prayers.

51:08.858 --> 51:10.151
Yes, ma'am.
We won't.

51:10.234 --> 51:11.861
<i>Your services
are no longer needed--</i>

51:11.944 --> 51:13.112
Look.

51:14.489 --> 51:16.407
<i>- Oh!</i>
- Oh, damn.

51:22.997 --> 51:25.124
Keep this closed
and don't open it for anyone.

51:26.584 --> 51:27.919
One inch thick.
Can stop a shotgun

51:28.002 --> 51:30.004
at point-blank range.

51:30.088 --> 51:31.380
Does it need to?

51:31.464 --> 51:33.216
Hasn't happened
in a couple years.

51:33.299 --> 51:35.843
If you have to pee, wait
till no one's in the store,

51:35.927 --> 51:37.845
come out, lock the front,
and then do your business.

51:37.929 --> 51:39.680
No lunch break,
but owner doesn't mind

51:39.764 --> 51:40.765
if you eat a burrito

51:40.848 --> 51:43.017
or whatever.

51:43.101 --> 51:44.102
You got it?

51:44.185 --> 51:45.228
Yeah, I think so.

51:45.311 --> 51:46.437
Darian comes in at 6:00.

51:46.521 --> 51:49.690
He's late sometimes,
but he'll show.

51:49.774 --> 51:53.653
<i>♪♪ I'm taking my time
before this life ends ♪♪</i>

51:53.736 --> 51:56.489
<i>♪♪ I've been giving
everything ♪♪</i>

51:56.572 --> 51:58.533
<i>♪♪ I'm taking my time ♪♪</i>

51:58.616 --> 52:00.910
<i>♪♪ Before this life ends ♪♪</i>

52:07.458 --> 52:12.296
<i>♪♪ I've been giving
everything I love ♪♪</i>

52:14.257 --> 52:15.550
<i>♪♪ It's so good ♪♪</i>

52:17.593 --> 52:19.595
Hey.
The fuck's wrong with you?

52:19.679 --> 52:21.389
Leave me alone, Carl.

52:21.472 --> 52:26.144
<i>♪♪ Silly self-made man ♪♪</i>

52:28.062 --> 52:32.984
<i>♪♪ Got 18 castles
in the sand ♪♪</i>

52:33.067 --> 52:37.071
<i>♪♪ Without a love
it's no good ♪♪</i>

52:37.155 --> 52:42.118
<i>♪♪ It's no good ♪♪</i>

52:43.828 --> 52:45.872
She doesn't love me.

52:45.955 --> 52:47.665
Who?

52:47.748 --> 52:49.500
Kelly.

52:50.501 --> 52:52.420
I tried to kiss her,
and she...

52:57.508 --> 53:00.219
Why can't anyone ever love me?

53:00.303 --> 53:02.847
Come on.
That's not true.

53:02.930 --> 53:04.473
It is.

53:04.557 --> 53:06.058
Franny loves you.

53:06.142 --> 53:08.144
That doesn't fucking count.

53:11.981 --> 53:13.858
Someone shot at me today.

53:13.941 --> 53:14.942
What?

53:15.026 --> 53:17.028
Yeah, at work.

53:17.111 --> 53:18.988
I fucked him up.

53:19.697 --> 53:20.698
The cops come?

53:20.781 --> 53:22.950
Yeah.
Said I did a good job,

53:23.034 --> 53:25.828
but probably should've
just given him the money.

53:25.912 --> 53:27.663
It was only, like, 120 bucks.

53:29.373 --> 53:31.876
No shit.
You don't want

53:31.959 --> 53:33.711
to take a bullet
for Captain Bob.

53:35.004 --> 53:36.672
Guess I just kind of went crazy
on the dude

53:36.756 --> 53:39.008
after Kelly broke up with me,

53:39.091 --> 53:42.595
and getting that rejection
letter from West Point.

53:43.429 --> 53:45.681
You got a letter
from West Point?

53:45.765 --> 53:47.475
Yeah.

53:47.558 --> 53:50.061
Didn't even make it past
the first cut.

53:50.144 --> 53:54.857
<i>♪♪ My moves
are a never-ending smile ♪♪</i>

53:54.941 --> 53:56.901
Sorry.

53:56.984 --> 53:58.236
Yeah.

53:58.319 --> 53:59.528
Me, too.

54:00.780 --> 54:03.157
You know you'll find somebody.

54:03.241 --> 54:05.117
You think so?

54:05.201 --> 54:07.286
Yeah, definitely.

54:07.370 --> 54:10.122
Kelly's a bitch.
She likes to break hearts.

54:10.206 --> 54:11.749
She is a bitch.

54:13.459 --> 54:15.753
Yeah, we should go
fuck her up.

54:15.836 --> 54:18.839
She'd kick both our asses.

54:22.635 --> 54:25.263
I'm glad you didn't get shot.

54:25.346 --> 54:27.390
Yeah, me too.

54:39.402 --> 54:40.861
Is that Jesus?

54:49.662 --> 54:51.455
Here you go.

54:51.539 --> 54:53.249
Thanks.

55:04.510 --> 55:05.928
Fiona?

55:07.847 --> 55:09.348
Holy fuck.

55:11.726 --> 55:12.935
Hi, Max.

55:15.438 --> 55:16.689
$8.52.

55:19.191 --> 55:20.192
How've you been?

55:22.903 --> 55:24.238
I've been better.

55:24.322 --> 55:25.656
Yeah.

55:28.034 --> 55:30.328
Uh, listen,
I was meaning to call you.

55:30.411 --> 55:32.621
The zoning on that lot you're
a partner in got approved.

55:32.705 --> 55:35.833
Looks like the nursing
home's still gonna purchase it.

55:35.916 --> 55:37.668
You know, we still have
some due diligence to do,

55:37.752 --> 55:40.504
but should close the next six,
maybe 12 months.

55:42.298 --> 55:44.425
And can I get 50 bucks on six?

55:44.508 --> 55:45.676
Uh...

55:48.804 --> 55:50.056
I don't remember
exactly how much

55:50.139 --> 55:51.140
you have in the partnership.

55:51.223 --> 55:52.767
Something around $90,000?

55:54.018 --> 55:55.311
It's $100,000.

55:58.814 --> 56:00.566
What if I bought you out now?

56:03.069 --> 56:04.320
- What?
- Yeah.

56:04.403 --> 56:05.613
That way, you don't have to
wait a year

56:05.696 --> 56:06.739
for your money,
and I don't have

56:06.822 --> 56:08.824
to waste my time
hunting down your next of kin

56:08.908 --> 56:11.285
after you get shot selling
cheap wine out of this box.

56:13.579 --> 56:15.247
Still have
the same phone number?

56:15.331 --> 56:16.540
Yeah.

56:16.624 --> 56:18.084
Good.

56:19.710 --> 56:21.337
I'll call you in the morning.
We'll get it done.

56:39.939 --> 56:42.817
<i>♪♪ I wake up ♪♪</i>

56:42.900 --> 56:45.027
<i>♪♪ Waiting for you ♪♪</i>

56:45.111 --> 56:46.821
<i>♪♪ I try ♪♪</i>

56:49.949 --> 56:52.868
- Got it?
- Yup, I got this one.

57:01.168 --> 57:02.670
Let's go.

57:15.808 --> 57:16.976
Hello?

57:21.897 --> 57:23.357
Hello!

57:27.611 --> 57:29.572
Fuck.

57:31.157 --> 57:33.909
<i>♪♪ Wake up waiting for you ♪♪</i>

57:35.995 --> 57:38.622
<i>♪♪ I try hard ♪♪</i>

57:38.706 --> 57:42.126
<i>♪♪ To start anew ♪♪</i>

57:42.209 --> 57:45.171
<i>♪♪ I'm drowning
in the deep blue ♪♪</i>

57:45.254 --> 57:48.132
<i>♪♪ Swam by underground ♪♪</i>

57:48.215 --> 57:50.509
<i>♪♪ And I'm trying hard ♪♪</i>

57:50.593 --> 57:54.597
<i>♪♪ To be kind ♪♪</i>

57:54.680 --> 57:59.602
<i>♪♪ But the world just
leaves me blind ♪♪</i>
